// CHANGELOG v9.9.2 → v9.9.3
// ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
// Patch #28: CHoCH gate relaxed from OPEN → CAUTION-ok.
//            CHoCH fires as consolidation breaks — requiring OPEN (composite
//            >= 70) blocked it on the exact bars it should render. BOS keeps
//            OPEN. CIE gate_structure_break(is_choch) API: CHoCH call sites
//            pass true. Requires GodTier_ContextEngine v1.4.0 / published v6.
// Patch #29: ZZ ATR Reversal Multiplier default 1.5 → 1.0.
//            Reduces required swing reversal from ~$450-600 to ~$300 on
//            BTC 15m. ZZ was freezing in consolidation, starving L1 and
//            making BOS/CHoCH geometrically impossible mid-session.
// Patch #30: stacked_imb_count decoupled from show_stacked_imb toggle.
//            Count feeds CIE L3. show_stacked_imb was zeroing the L3 input
//            when boxes were disabled, suppressing FVG/IFVG gate downstream.
