// CHANGELOG v9.9.1 → v9.9.2
// ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
// Patch #17: varip for tick_counter — var was resetting to confirmed-bar
//            value on each tick, making the realtime throttle gate count
//            bars instead of ticks. varip preserves value across ticks.
// Patch #18: Removed _abs_atr = ta.atr(14) in absorption block → current_atr
// Patch #19: Removed _div_atr = ta.atr(14) in divergence block → current_atr
// Patch #20: Removed _smd_atr = ta.atr(14) in SMD block → current_atr
//            Patches 18-20: patches #12/13/15 had each introduced a redundant
