// Patch #21: f_smart_money_div() now accepts float atr parameter — removes
//            the last hidden ta.atr(14) call inside the function body.
//            Call site updated: f_smart_money_div(eff_smd_lookback, current_atr)
// Patch #22: VWAD block — for [k, buy_v] in map replaces keys+get pattern
// Patch #23: Live POC block — for [key, vol] in map, removes keys allocation
//            in the realtime hot path (runs on every tick via execute_now)
// Patch #24: Pruning helpers f_prune_labels/lines/boxes() — 16 two-line
//            while/delete/shift blocks replaced with typed single-line calls
// Patch #25: array.from() for LTF null guards — 15 lines → 5 lines
// Patch #26: Exhaustion detection rewritten — detect_exhaustion() loop
//            telescopes to arr[last] - arr[0], making the 20-element rolling
//            arrays delta_history/price_history equivalent to close[4] and
//            cumulative_delta[4]. Both var arrays and array.clear() session
