// CHANGELOG v9.9.1 — Audit Patch Release
// ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
// Patch #1:  compression_trigger_reason catch-all → "Controller" (was unreliable ternary)
//            alertcondition Threshold expanded to include "Controller" label
// Patch #2:  Removed duplicate session_age declaration inside barstate.islast (shadow var)
// Patch #6:  ifvg_count_prev sync decoupled from show_fvg gate — prevents spurious
//            IFVG flip signal after show_fvg toggle off/on mid-session
// Patch #7:  va_state newSession reset "Stable" → "Neutral" — amber early-session
