// -------------------------------------------------------------------------
// 🏷️ LABEL VISIBILITY INPUTS  (v9.7.0)
// -------------------------------------------------------------------------
// Tier 1 — hardcoded ON (no input): SWEEP+FA, CHoCH, FAIL BULL/BEAR, ZZ SWEEP.
//           These are your primary scalping signals — never hidden.
// Tier 2 — ON by default, user-toggleable. Cut caps to 20 each.
// Tier 3 — OFF by default. Noisy on NQ 1m/5m. Data still feeds dashboard.
